PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1:

Unmasked SF mayor, London Breed, says she was "feeling the spirit," didn't care about mask at indoor party. Scott Gottlieb admits CDC 6-foot distancing rule was made up. Emmys held maskless in small room with masked servants. Biden disasters: Afghanistan, France, boosters. Buck's booster theory. Catastrophe on border as thousands of Haitians gather under bridge. Milley lied about Afghanistan drone strike.
